These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
City: boston, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| City   | paris | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, australian
1. the canadian is on the left or right of the australian##3
2. the australian is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Nationality   | canadian | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, drama
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | horror |

 #################################

 
